CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 9, 1962, pg. 7, reads: "Fraternal Leaders Feted - Members of Annma Valley 84, OES, honored during a banquet reception at Allen Chapel AME Church. Guests at the head table include the honoree, Mr. Coleman; Mrs. Louella Jackson, W. M.; Mrs. Ester Green, G. W. M.; Alfred Burrell, Mrs. Anna Williams and Herbert Townes, P. G. M., standing. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men and women, including Solomon Coleman, Louella Jackson, Esther Green, Alfred Burrell, Anna Williams, and Herbert Townes, at banquet, Allen Chapel AME Church
